  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546940/extras/9a14a1919a995e2a051892fc076c4ff4.apng?t=1738204157\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546940/extras/9a14a1919a995e2a051892fc076c4ff4.poster.avif?t=1738204157\" class=\"bb_img\" width=594 height=69 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BOINKGAME is a precision platformer where the only enemy is yourself. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And the walls... The walls are a bigger enemy actually.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump carefully through 12 screens and try to reach the trophy at the top! Don't worry if you bonk into a wall and lose some progress. You're always improving. :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546940/extras/a7b894b2131a289fef9b529ee9fca964.apng?t=1738204157\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546940/extras/a7b894b2131a289fef9b529ee9fca964.poster.avif?t=1738204157\" class=\"bb_img\" width=594 height=69 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jumping</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bonking (four unique sounds!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-game timer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No saving</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546940/extras/9a14a1919a995e2a051892fc076c4ff4.apng?t=1738204157\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546940/extras/9a14a1919a995e2a051892fc076c4ff4.poster.avif?t=1738204157\" class=\"bb_img\" width=594 height=69 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BOINKGAME is a precision platformer where the only enemy is yourself. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And the walls... The walls are a bigger enemy actually.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump carefully through 12 screens and try to reach the trophy at the top! Don't worry if you bonk into a wall and lose some progress. You're always improving. :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546940/extras/a7b894b2131a289fef9b529ee9fca964.apng?t=1738204157\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546940/extras/a7b894b2131a289fef9b529ee9fca964.poster.avif?t=1738204157\" class=\"bb_img\" width=594 height=69 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jumping</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bonking (four unique sounds!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-game timer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No saving</p></li></ul>",
